<div class="container">
	<h1>Contact Me!</h1>
</div>
<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-8 col-md-6">
			{{#if enquirySubmitted}}
			<h3>Thanks for getting in touch.</h3>
			{{else}}
			<form method="post">
				<input type="hidden" name="action" value="contact">
				<div class="form-group {{#if validationErrors.name}}has-error{{/if}}">
					<label>Name</label>
					<input type="text" name="name.full"  class="form-control" value="{{formData.[name.full]}}">
				</div>
				<div class="form-group {{#if validationErrors.email}}has-error{{/if}}">
					<label>Email</label>
					<input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" value="{{formData.email}}">
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
					<label>Phone</label>
					<input type="text" name="phone" placeholder="(optional)" class="form-control" value="{{formData.phone}}">
				</div>
				<div class="form-group {{#if validationErrors.enquiryType}}has-error{{/if}}">
					<label>What are you contacting us about?</label>
					<select name="enquiryType" class="form-control">
						<option value="">(select one)</option>
						{{#each enquiryTypes}}
						<option value="{{value}}">{{label}}</option>
						{{/each}}
					</select>
				</div>
				<div class="form-group {{#if validationErrors.message}}has-error{{/if}} ">
					<label>Message</label>
					<textarea name="message" placeholder="Leave us a message..." rows="4" class="form-control">{{formData.message}}</textarea>
				</div>
				<div class="form-actions">
					<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send</button>
				</div>
			</form>
			{{/if}}
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-4 col-md-6">
			<h3>Other Ways To Keep Up:</h3>
			<p>For keeping up with my exploits, reading my all-caps rants, seeing the semi-cool stuff I find, or saying hi, check me on the tweets.</p>
			<ul><li><a href="https://twitter.com/andrewthewhip">@AndrewTheWhip</a></li></ul>
			<p>For reading rants and seeing what kinds of questionably funny/certainly geeky stuff I like, follow me on my real Tumblr.</p>
			<ul><li><a href="https://andrewthewhip.tumblr.com">andrewthewhip.tumblr.com</a></li></ul>
			<p>For watching me sing songs and talk very quickly, subscribe to me on YouTube.</p>
			<ul><li><a href="https://youtube.com/theandrewwhipple">youtube.com/theandrewwhipple</a></li></ul>
			
			
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

